---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home">
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h1 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Computational Epidemiology & Bioinformatics Lab</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #475569; max-width: 800px;">
            We leverage high-dimensional data, multi-omics frameworks, and scalable machine learning pipelines to model complex disease risks and population health patterns.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
        <div>
            <h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">Research Focus</h2>
            <p>Our group works at the intersection of statistics and biology, utilizing massive biobank datasets to uncover rare variant associations and develop robust stability selection methodologies.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Latest News</h3>
            <ul style="padding-left: 1.2rem; margin: 0; color: #475569;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>May 2026:</strong> New preprint on pipeline optimization released.</li>
                <li><strong>Mar 2026:</strong> Group awarded a new grant for multi-omics integration.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>